Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:05.47,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:08.18,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged a vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:13.36,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:18.49,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:31.17,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The future that the forbidden fruit foretells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:39.67,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change the dream into reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:51.56,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The ending that everybody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:54.73,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.81,0:00:57.52,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged our vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:01:02.36,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.57,0:01:07.87,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someday I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.87,0:01:17.17,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bright and ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.84,0:01:26.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The human whose name is written\Nin this note shall die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.22,0:01:29.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:32.81,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz26.964\move(487,416,499,417,0,1663)}Takuo Shibuimaru\NAccidental Death
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:32.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Stop!\N- Now let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:32.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:38.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note is real!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:46.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think for a moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:49.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that any human who's used the\NDeath Note can go to Heaven, or Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:53.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want the world to know...\Nof my existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:56.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That there is someone is\Npassing judgment on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:01:58.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will become...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:01.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the god of this new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:11.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea what he was thinking,\Nso I'm through with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:14.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then how was it\Nwith that other old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:16.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:18.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please translate that sentence\Ninto Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:19.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.07,0:02:25.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"When finally, he fully succeeded\Nin making his dream a reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:30.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he was immersed in beatitude."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:32.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:36.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, a perfect answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:43.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, class is dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:50.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:53.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,School sure is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:55.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:02:59.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:02.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Others can hear my voice\Nwhen I talk unlike yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:05.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:07.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Light! We're going to go--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:09.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:12.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have anything to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:15.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you just going home\Nlike you usually do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:18.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NI have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:22.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:26.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada is suspected of stabbing\Na fellow employee in the abdomen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:29.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,at a restaurant in Kabukicho,\NShinjuku, yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:33.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The knife was from the restaurant\Nand was roughly twelve inches long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:35.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey!\N- The suspect said...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:37.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, Light!\N- "he was being rude, so I just lost it."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:38.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:41.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are working very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:44.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't waste any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:47.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I only have a limited amount of time\Nto write names in the notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:51.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only time I have is when I get\Nhome from school and until I go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:54.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also need to maintain my grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:56.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep during class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:04:00.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do all of my homework\Nfor school and my prep classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:02.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lack of sleep is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll affect my health and concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:09.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm trying to change\Nthis world into a utopia without evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's never enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.68,0:04:17.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why did you lock the door, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:18.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:19.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me with my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on quadratic equations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:32.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry if you were studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:35.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...it just doesn't make\Nany sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:38.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:40.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:44.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Any human who touches\Nthe notebook in your drawer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,will be able to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:51.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He waits to tell me that\Ncrucial detail now? Damn Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:53.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:58.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what exactly\Ndon't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:00.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:01.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:04.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From what we know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:06.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there have been 52 deaths\Njust this past week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:08.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They all had heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:13.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all criminals who were wanted\Nor being held in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:17.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are probably other criminals\Nwhose deaths are still unaccounted for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:20.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean the death toll\Ncould easily be over a hundred?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:27.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief...we've already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:30.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.\NI had a call from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:32.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:34.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they were all criminals who\Nprobably would have been executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:36.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps we shouldn't\Nconcern ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:37.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:40.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if\Nthey're criminals or on death row.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:41.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing them is murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:44.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't even sure that\Nthey were murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.85,0:05:47.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way over 100 people\Ncould have heart attacks at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:49.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It has got to be murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:54.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it even possible to kill\Nthat many people at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:58.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We believe that a large organization\Ncarefully orchestrated these killings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say a large organization is involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:04.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but think that\Nthe FBI or CIA is involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I dare you to say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:09.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.\NLet's stop joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:12.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to first clarify if these\Nare murders,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,or strange coincidences.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:15.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't all the autopsy reports\Nsay that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:18.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the deaths were caused\Nby inexplicable heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:22.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see what else can be learned\Nfrom just the way they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:27.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be worth looking into\Nif they were stabbed with knives!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,\Nwe'll just have to have L solve this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, what is L?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:44.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your first time at\Nthis conference, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:49.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows L's name, location\Nor what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:53.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's managed to solve every case\Nhe's taken, no matter how difficult it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:57.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's cracked many of\Nthe world's unsolved cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:58.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's our trump card,\Nthe ace in the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:00.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our last hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:08.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't L an arrogant individual who'll\Nonly take on cases he's interested in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:10.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't even contact him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:15.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L is already involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:30.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L is already investigating this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:32.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:34.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:37.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the only man who can contact L.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, Watari's identity\Nis also unknown...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:45.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L will now speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Members of the ICPO...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:54.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am L.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:08:01.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we doing sneaking around\Nin such a desolate place, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:05.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People who touch the Death Note\Ncan see you, can't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:09.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just walk around with\Nsomething this dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:13.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, I thought that if\Nmy family saw the notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:16.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could pass it off as\Na record of cases
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:19.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,which I'm using to study\Nto become a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:22.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm walking a fine line\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:24.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not careful,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I might end up killing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,my own family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:38.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This case is unprecedented\Nin scope and difficulty because...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:39.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it involves more people than\Nany other case has before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:45.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is also an unforgivable crime\Nof serial murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:48.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to solve this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:53.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I need the ICPO... no, various\Nworldwide organizations, to cooperate fully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:58.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to decide whether\Nyou'll support me at this conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:03.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...I strongly desire to work\Nwith the Japanese Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:04.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:06.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:09.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of how many\Nsuspects there are,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:12.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a strong possibility\Nthey're Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:16.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they aren't Japanese,\Nthey are hiding in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:17.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What grounds do you\Nhave for your claims?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:20.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:24.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can show you very soon\Nby directly confronting the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A direct confrontation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:31.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I would like set up\Nheadquarters in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:39.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was pretty easy to make...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:42.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Does that mean you\Nwere able to hide the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:45.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, in this drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:48.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that count as a hiding place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:51.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You left the key in the lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:52.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:56.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better that I intentionally\Nleft the key in a noticeable place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:01.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a regular diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:06.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people will probably be satisfied\Nwith the secrets of this drawer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:08.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,after reading this diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:09.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:12.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The real key... is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:16.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing suspicious\Nabout having one of these on my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:18.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a regular ballpoint pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:19.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the ink cartridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:21.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:22.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:24.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On the back of the drawer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:26.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a small hole that's hard to notice\Nif you don't look closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You put this in the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:36.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.\NIt's got a false bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:40.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you also have the fake diary,\Nso I doubt anyone will find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:41.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they discovered\Nit has a false bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:48.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there would be no way that\Nthey could take the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:51.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:55.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This ink cartridge is an insulator\Nso it doesn't channel electricity,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:57.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and stops the flow of electricity\Nin the circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:10:59.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When the bottom of this drawer is closed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:02.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this piece of rubber also\Nstops the flow of electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:06.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if someone were to\Nforce open the bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:10.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,gasoline in thin plastic bags\Nwill ignite at that moment and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:14.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the notebook will instantly\Nbe set aflame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:17.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All evidence will be\Ncompletely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it's set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:21.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can just say the reason\NI burned it was that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:25.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"l didn't want anyone to\Nsee my real diary."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:27.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a believable excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:29.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a notebook, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard when a human\Ngets a Death Note,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:36.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the biggest problem they have is\Nfinding a good place to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:41.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Light, you're probably\Nthe first to go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:44.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that setup is really dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:46.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make even\Nthe slightest mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:48.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you could be badly burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:52.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dangerous?\NYou're talking nonsense again, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:55.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been putting myself\Nin danger from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:58.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I first got a hold\Nof the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:02.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to that,\Nthis is hardly dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:05.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, quite the opposite.\NIt protects me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:08.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is better?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:11.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A small fire in the house,\Nor being executed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:26.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, within\Nthe Tokyo West Penitentiary,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:32.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoki Kurotsukayama, aged thirty-two,\Nwho was detained for armed robbery...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:34.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is reported to have\Ndied of a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:38.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In response to the endless,\Nbizarre deaths of prisoners...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:41.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing...\NBad guys just keep dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:44.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little scary, but it does feel great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, we really can't\Ndo anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:48.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the police are behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:50.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police don't have that kind of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:51.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:52.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? About who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:55.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira... Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who's going to be killed next...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:01.29,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(178,125)\frz8.575\pos(296,214)}Kira, kill everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:02.42,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,231)}Do you want to send this message?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:02.42,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,366)}Send
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:06.59,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz17.729\frx10\fry14\pos(477,142)}Name: Rococo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:06.59,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz30.023\pos(418,314)\frx6\fry12}{pos(427,315)}Kira, kill everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:06.59,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz50.398\pos(594,365)\frx358\fry30}Name: Misery
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk, take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:06.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:09.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's already created a website.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:13.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"The legend of Kira the savior."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:16.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty cool.\NIs this about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:17.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:20.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kira" seems to come from\Nthe English word "killer."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:25.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become "Kira" to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:30.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just searching the word "Kira," and\Ncountless sites like this one appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:36.91,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz336.73\move(342,117,341,182,0,931)}Deepening Mystery Causes Controversy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:36.40,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz336.028\move(224,124,222,304,19,2563)}Mysterious Deaths in Prisons Continue
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:34.15,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz337.453\move(442,94,438,370,0,3978)}Reconsidering the\NInvestigative System
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:32.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Television and newspapers have\Nonly publicized
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:36.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"the successive, mysterious deaths\Nof vicious criminals."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:40.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the people of the world\Ncan already feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:43.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The existence of someone\Npassing judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:48.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk, humans are like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:52.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, there's no way that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:56.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,anyone would bring up the topic of\Nkilling bad people in homeroom at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:14:00.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if someone were to bring it up,\Neveryone would act pious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:02.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:04.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they're bound to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:07.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's the right thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:12.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans must put up a front\Nlike that in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:14.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But their true feelings are there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:19.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They may be afraid or not acknowledge\Nmy existence on the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:23.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but on the internet,\Nwhere one can remain anonymous...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:24.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is already thriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:29.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't talk about it,\Nbut they all understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:32.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is making\Nthe bad guys disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:38.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who have a clean conscience\Nare cheering for Kira in their hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:39.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And those who have done wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:42.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,fear that heaven's judgment\Nwill strike upon them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:45.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:48.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going exactly as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:50.32,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(318,146)}Notice
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:50.32,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(324,378)}The Scheduled Program will be\Ninterrupted for a Special Broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:53.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We interrupt this program to\Nbring you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:57.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a special, worldwide broadcast from\Nthe ICPO, Interpol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:59.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:01.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Interpol?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:02.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:06.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Lind L. Tailor
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:09.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the sole person able to\Nmobilize the world's police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:12.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also known as L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:15.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:17.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally started.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:21.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's never shown his face, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that L is serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:27.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, L...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:29.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing exactly\Nwhat you told us to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:33.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's see you prove what\Nyou said at the ICPO conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There has been a string of serial killings\Ntargeting criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:42.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the most atrocious act of murder\Nin history and it will not go unpunished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely catch\Nthe one behind the murders,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:48.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,commonly known as "Kira."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:50.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'll definitely catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:54.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fool.\NThere's no way he can catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Death Note!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:16:00.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have this,\Nthere's no evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:03.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:07.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that the police would\Nstart investigating
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:09.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and that someone like you\Nwould turn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:15.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, I have a pretty good idea behind\Nyour motive and why you're doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:19.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what you're doing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:19.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:24.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:27.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:30.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saving the meek, who fear evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:32.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man who will become...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:33.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the god of the ideal, new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:37.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All those who oppose that god...\Nthey are evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:41.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L, you're too stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:45.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This could've been more interesting\Nif you'd been a bit smarter...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:03.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire world is watching
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:07.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to see what happens if\Nanyone defies me...L.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:13.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just five more seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:14.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:15.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:16.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:18.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:32.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\NWhy don't you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:39.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:41.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to check to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:43.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought\Nyou could have done this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:48.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, it seems you can kill people\Nwithout direct contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:52.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't believe it before\Nseeing it with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:55.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:18:00.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just killed the man on-screen,\NLind L. Tailor,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:04.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you just killed a man who was\Nscheduled to be executed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:06.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:07.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This criminal is someone who\Nthe police caught secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:13.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His capture wasn't broadcast\Non television or the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:18.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that even you\Ncouldn't get information on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:21.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:24.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I, L... do exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:28.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So come on!\NTry and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:34.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's wrong? Do it quickly!\N- What's going on?! This is unreal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:36.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- C'mon! Kill me!\N- Are you trying to die, L?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:39.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's going on?\N- It's Kira versus L!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:40.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a live murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Come on, Kira!\N- This is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:43.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Try and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:46.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Can't you do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:54.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you can't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:18:58.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there are some people\Nthat you can't kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:01.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've given me a good clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:06.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you something good in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:10.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that this is\Na live broadcast worldwide, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:13.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is only being broadcast\Nin the Kanto region of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:17.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning on broadcasting this\Nin different areas at different times,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:19.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems that I no longer need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:22.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I know that you are based\Nin the Kanto region.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:25.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This L guy is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:29.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The first victim was\Nthe killer in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:33.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police overlooked this case\Nbecause it was so minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:36.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the criminals who\Ndied of heart attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:39.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this one's crime\Nwas the least serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:39.98,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(111,213)}Kurou Otoharada (42)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:39.98,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(168,110)}Unemployed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:39.98,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(316,378)}Shinjuku Random Killing Incident
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:42.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, his crime was
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:43.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,only broadcast in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:43.94,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz19.319\pos(292,295)\fad(0,459)}Kurou Otoharada
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:46.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been able to deduce this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:54.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are in Japan and\Nyour first victim was your guinea pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:20:00.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just lucky that you're in Kanto,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:02.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the most heavily populated region\Nin Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:07.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that things\Nwould go quite so well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:12.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, it won't be too long\Nbefore I can sentence you to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:16.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L certainly lives up\Nto his reputation...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:18.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's proved that\NKira exists,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:22.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that the killings took place,\Nand that Kira's in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:28.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, I'm interested how\Nyou commit the murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:32.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'll find that out\Nwhen I catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:36.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we meet again...\NKira...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:47.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:51.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,sentence me to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:56.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.\NI'll accept your challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:00.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They both have to hunt down\Neach other,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:02.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but neither of them know\Neach other's name or face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:05.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the first one who gets\Nfound is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:08.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans sure are interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:10.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:11.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:15.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- I will definitely find and finish you!\N- I will definitely find and finish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:16.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:17.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:19.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- justice!\N- justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:28.17,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I dreamed a dream that no one could see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:33.55,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I threw away everything that I didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:42.56,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm holding these feelings\Nthat I can't give up in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:48.94,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Even if my feet fall victim\Nto the shackles of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:53.53,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}In between reality and my ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:59.24,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I can't hold back the flooding impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:06.67,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Because I have a strong desire\Nto accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.29,0:22:11.88,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:22.64,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm not weak enough to believe\Nany of these negative perceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.10,0:22:28.44,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm a trickster who doesn't know solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:37.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the one who's going to find L.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.74,0:22:39.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police will track him down...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.24,0:22:40.79,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz326.493\pos(434,149)}Serial Murder\NSpecial\NInvestigation\NHeadquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:41.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will eliminate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.66,0:22:45.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I may be able to provide\Nyou a little more entertainment, Ryuk.
